sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor S as Student
    participant F as Frontend (React)
    participant B as Backend (FastAPI)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant AI as OpenRouter API (Gemini)

    S->>F: Clicks "Break Down with AI" on a task
    F->>B: POST /stms/ai/split-task
    B->>DB: Fetch original task details
    DB-->>B: Return task title & description
    B->>AI: Send prompt with task details
    AI-->>B: Return list of sub-tasks (JSON)
    B->>DB: Save new sub-tasks to database
    DB-->>B: Confirm saved
    B-->>F: Return list of new sub-tasks
    F-->>S: Display new sub-tasks in UI
